c31f04e94ee48fcf337","tid":738400,"uid":45368,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T17:12:45.000Z","msg":"台灣長住同旅遊始終有分別，考慮清楚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T01:17:15.000Z","msg":"始終地方大,住又住得舒適啲！係搵嘢做嗰方面煩啫"},{"pid":"37ded3f5b844b96352e07195f2eb3e64b398eb9d","tid":738400,"uid":5297,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63bd06449a6967fc627e77ab3b93b0e2ee62a235","tid":738400,"uid":6484,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"b446d2522883cbe62ee5f234b4d3311aec825b43","tid":738400,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"你個收入會大概差幾遠?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T13:31:15.000Z","msg":"而家我2xk一個月 睇佣幾多<br />\n過到去唔做返呢行 有40k台幣已經算好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T01:28:47.000Z","msg":"2xk過到去都係2xk<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f8db057adb0f0bf16d0a28acf0c0825318bffd","tid":738400,"uid":20241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T02:02:37.000Z","msg":"台灣好難搵寫字樓工<br />\n大部分都係低賤體力工/服務業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc613c23be25f504a8b499a187f45fd1810298a","tid":738400,"uid":178317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"台灣邊到先"},{"pid":"67a1288500adfcfe8b93aa4a81732949fb080b66","tid":738400,"uid":37672,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"441f457855de16581d7d1397205067b3492e0041","tid":738400,"uid":6484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"究竟cv重要定生活重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"人生為生活啦下嘛<br />\n<br />\n你係香港5萬一個月 又係買唔到樓 生活上最基本既保障都攞唔到<br />\n<br />\n你係果度皮幾野 開心又快活 二，三百萬既樓你會知道你努力係買到 唔係接觸唔到既野<br />\n<br />\n香港淪陷時間問題，有機會就狠下心走啦！<br />\n<br />\n世世代代移民第一代邊個唔係涯架啫。係咪先？<br />\n<br />\n我走左架啦 本來香港做地盤18k，而家係日本做餐廳9-10k 但我過得開心過係香港。而且呢度兩百萬 3房新樓。我會覺得涯係有意義。"},{"pid":"c605857e16114c06e3d64edf1cee04b90e3ee8f3","tid":738400,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:59:07.000Z","msg":"移民台灣冇你想像中咁好 <br />\n<br />\n只係肯儲錢都叫買到樓<br />\n<br />\n小左收入你好可能會唔習慣 <br />\n<br />\n例如會小左旅行 小左換電話 等等"},{"pid":"8851a6ec14f6c42b1a296088428b4d1fe74c7085","tid":738400,"uid":29703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"另一半點樣？ 仲有屋企人點算"},{"pid":"ad561ed1bd8f53e3a4aa306bb3297d1408306670","tid":738400,"uid":46407,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"最中問題係你搵到咩工 本身做果樣唔係專業 有牌既 去到你搵得唔多 地方又唔慣 你可能都想返黎"},{"pid":"e8ffd8d2597cf6a232c1e7bfad0aad693bf4cdae","tid":738400,"uid":192361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"如果你台灣搵到80KNT 一個月你會生活得好開心。"},{"pid":"9cddb769f9b66acee61db38aca5f094820e2c0b3","tid":738400,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"我幾年前25歲左右搵15k, 都有個5萬台幣既offer, 我都怕前境唔好留低, 叫公司加到我22k就算<br />\n而家香港條path都仲ok<br />\n去台灣應該係中年既事<br />\n真係怕而家去, 到時30尾40頭想返香港俾人壓價壓到仆街"},{"pid":"d27db1320381c66590dd8a35eb93e327637ec7ee","tid":738400,"uid":170436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"就黎30 。香港做緊d唔專業既工，2X -3Xk 一個月<br />\n都諗緊結婚之後去唔去台灣<br />\n去到個邊既人工有40k  都偷笑，仲要當兵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b87076bdb5b34678428fd96e2aea199e659996","tid":738400,"uid":109102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"當兵都係一個concern咁就放棄過去嘅念頭啦"},{"pid":"60e3588e66b8fc80af7e748938c8979c516f75a2","tid":738400,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"住邊到先？台北台南生活已經分別好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab79393fcd4132378fd2022adbf02edb4fa7e31b","tid":738400,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score